<div class="container py-4">
    <h1 class="mb-4">About CSVUpload</h1>

    <p>
        CSVUpload is a simple ASP.NET Core MVC application that allows users to upload CSV files,
        preview the data, and store it in a database.
    </p>

    <p>
        Features of CSVUpload include:
    </p>

    <ul>
        <li>Upload CSV files with columns: Name, Email, Address, About, Number</li>
        <li>Preview the first 10 rows of the CSV before import</li>
        <li>Store uploaded users in a database</li>
        <li>View all uploaded users in a sortable and searchable table</li>
        <li>Download CSV template for quick start</li>
        <li>Responsive design using Bootstrap 5</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
        This page serves as a demonstration of integrating CSV uploads with ASP.NET Core MVC.
        You can use this template to build more complex applications with file imports and data management.
    </p>

